precis:
Enactment of the PROVINCIAL EMERGENCIES FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 43 -
which (a) DECLARES the severe storm in NEWFOUNDLAND in January 2000 to be
of concern to the federal government, and (b) AUTHORIZES the provision of
financial assistance in respect thereof.
